00:04:59.380 --> 00:05:02.900
that's what we're going to
call phishing in my mind.

00:05:02.900 --> 00:05:04.970
We use the word
phishing in our title,

00:05:04.970 --> 00:05:09.430
you see it there, as a
metaphor for a broader

00:05:09.430 --> 00:05:11.220
range of deception.

00:05:11.220 --> 00:05:15.040
So think about Bing putting
that story on as the lead story.

00:05:15.040 --> 00:05:18.680
Is that really high
minded news reporting?

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:21.050
Well, to me it seems
