00:31:47.980 --> 00:31:49.582
And it was that sort of thing.

00:31:49.582 --> 00:31:51.040
Well, I'm giving
you some examples.

00:31:51.040 --> 00:31:52.290
We have many other examples.

00:31:52.290 --> 00:31:57.850
We attribute the financial
crisis recently to at least

00:31:57.850 --> 00:31:59.260
partly to phishing.

00:31:59.260 --> 00:32:02.655
People had the advantage of
