00:32:08.000 --> 00:32:12.500
That a lot of emotional tension
in life that people have

00:32:12.500 --> 00:32:14.730
is running out of
money and fearing

00:32:14.730 --> 00:32:19.230
for their possible
bankruptcy, and I

00:32:19.230 --> 00:32:22.120
think that marketing
